A tx´yan n-chi kub´ we´ tun t-xi t-xupin aju´ casco extzen n-xi´ t-xnaq´tza´n
joyb´aj. Te mankb´il n-chi kub´ we´, n-chi tzaj t-xo´n t-xu´k n-jaw we´,
